<font color="#ffffff">Why should she be punished?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">It's not fair.</font>

25:04.680 --> 25:06.200
<font color="#ffff00">You OK?</font>

25:08.280 --> 25:11.478
<font color="#ffffff">Feel so at home here among the dead.</font>

25:11.480 --> 25:14.238
<font color="#ffffff">Never bothered me.</font>

25:14.240 --> 25:15.718
<font color="#ffffff">But the dying...</font>

25:15.720 --> 25:19.320
<font color="#ffffff">No-one warned me this was going</font>
<font color="#ffffff">to be so difficult.</font>

25:21.680 --> 25:23.040
<font color="#ffff00">She's your mum.</font>

25:24.920 --> 25:27.998
<font color="#ffffff">You can't help thinking,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">"What would I would have become</font>

25:28.000 --> 25:31.400
<font color="#ffffff">"with a different mum,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">with a different upbringing?"</font>

25:32.800 --> 25:35.918
<font color="#ffffff">My mum gave me all that</font>
<font color="#ffffff">tough love when I was a child.</font>

25:35.920 --> 25:39.038
<font color="#ffffff">There was never</font>
<font color="#ffffff">any room for self-pity.</font>

25:39.040 --> 25:41.920
<font color="#ffffff">God knows what I would have</font>
<font color="#ffffff">ended up as if she hadn't.</font>

25:43.040 --> 25:46.998
<font color="#ffffff">School was tough,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">girls weren't always nice,</font>

25:47.000 --> 25:51.040
<font color="#ffffff">and the teachers were well-meaning.</font>

25:53.360 --> 25:57.158
<font color="#ffffff">I'd cry every day.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Didn't want to go.</font>

25:57.160 --> 26:00.598
<font color="#ffffff">Mum would just coax me</font>
<font color="#ffffff">through the school gates.</font>

26:00.600 --> 26:02.760
<font color="#ffffff">"Come on, it'll be all right."</font>

26:05.400 --> 26:07.758
<font color="#ffffff">Sweet weren't allowed at school.</font>

26:07.760 --> 26:09.878
<font color="#ffff00">Nothing fun ever was.</font>

26:09.880 --> 26:12.198
<font color="#ffffff">You'd get a detention if you were</font>
<font color="#ffffff">caught.</font>

26:12.200 --> 26:14.958
<font color="#ffffff">Before she left me every day,</font>

26:14.960 --> 26:17.678
<font color="#ffffff">Mum would slip a toffee</font>
<font color="#ffffff">into my pocket.</font>

26:17.680 --> 26:20.878
<font color="#ffffff">My fingers to her lip,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">and say, "Sh."</font>

26:20.880 --> 26:22.918
<font color="#ffffff">My day ever got too bad,</font>

26:22.920 --> 26:27.000
<font color="#ffffff">sneak that toffee out,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">and it was glorious.</font>

26:28.560 --> 26:32.918
<font color="#ffffff">And eat it and think of Mum,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">and it was like our little secret.</font>

26:32.920 --> 26:34.400
<font color="#ffffff">Our victory.</font>

26:37.320 --> 26:38.760
<font color="#ffff00">How is she?</font>

26:40.120 --> 26:41.400
<font color="#ffffff">Confused.</font>

26:42.680 --> 26:43.960
<font color="#ffffff">And in pain.</font>

26:46.120 --> 26:48.958
<font color="#ffffff">Makes me wonder why I'm putting</font>
<font color="#ffffff">her through it all.</font>

26:48.960 --> 26:51.720
<font color="#ffff00">You're doing</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the best you can for her.</font>

26:52.960 --> 26:54.520
<font color="#ffff00">You're a wonderful daughter.</font>

26:56.080 --> 26:57.360
<font color="#ffffff">WHISPERS: I'm not so sure.</font>

27:00.080 --> 27:03.478
<font color="#ffff00">Wonder who'll look after me</font>
<font color="#ffff00">when I'm an old lady.</font>

27:03.480 --> 27:05.400
<font color="#ffff00">Who will my Clarissa be?</font>

27:07.040 --> 27:09.918
<font color="#ffffff">We'll be looking after each other.</font>

27:09.920 --> 27:15.038
<font color="#ffffff">Drunk in an old people's home</font>
<font color="#ffffff">somewhere, giving the staff hell.</font>

27:15.040 --> 27:16.800
<font color="#ffffff">THEY CHUCKLE</font>

27:24.680 --> 27:26.598
<font color="#00ffff">Thought I was supposed</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to be the victim here.</font>

27:26.600 --> 27:29.158
<font color="#ffff00">I'm very sorry,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">but this is a murder enquiry.</font>

27:29.160 --> 27:32.238
<font color="#00ff00">Can't believe you're doing this.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">This is ludicrous.</font>

27:32.240 --> 27:34.958
<font color="#00ffff">I was only there because I got</font>
<font color="#00ffff">a note to meet somebody</font>

27:34.960 --> 27:37.198
<font color="#00ffff">about the baby.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">They didn't turn up.</font>

27:37.200 --> 27:40.438
<font color="#00ffff">They never do. </font><font color="#ffff00">Why didn't you</font>
<font color="#ffff00">mention this before?</font>

27:40.440 --> 27:42.078
<font color="#00ffff">Had a lot on my mind.</font>

27:42.080 --> 27:43.878
<font color="#ffff00">Can I have the note?</font>

27:43.880 --> 27:45.240
<font color="#00ffff">Yeah.</font>

27:50.000 --> 27:53.678
<font color="#00ffff">Not as often as they used to,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">but they still come, occasionally.</font>

27:53.680 --> 27:55.838
<font color="#00ffff">It was just another hoax.</font>

27:55.840 --> 27:57.640
<font color="#ffff00">Right. Can I have, erm...? </font><font color="#ffffff">Uh-huh.</font>

28:02.760 --> 28:04.160
<font color="#ffff00">Thank you.</font>

28:10.000 --> 28:11.720
<font color="#00ffff">I'm glad she's dead.</font>

28:15.560 --> 28:16.920
<font color="#ffffff">Sorry.</font>

28:18.800 --> 28:21.280
<font color="#ffffff">SHE BREATHES HEAVILY</font>

28:41.120 --> 28:42.318
<font color="#ffff00">You OK?</font>

28:42.320 --> 28:43.798
<font color="#ffffff">Yeah.</font>

28:43.800 --> 28:46.758
<font color="#ffffff">Just a bit light-headed, tired,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">that's all.</font>

28:46.760 --> 28:50.320
<font color="#ffff00">Shall I get you, erm...?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I don't need a nurse, Max.</font>

28:51.360 --> 28:52.880
<font color="#ffff00">I meant some chocolate.</font>

28:59.680 --> 29:01.518
<font color="#ffffff">Had one of those days today, Mum.</font>

29:01.520 --> 29:03.438
<font color="#ffffff">MUM GROANS</font>

29:03.440 --> 29:05.720
<font color="#ffffff">I guess your day</font>
<font color="#ffffff">wasn't much better.</font>

29:11.480 --> 29:13.558
<font color="#ffffff">If it's time to stop...</font>

29:13.560 --> 29:15.518
<font color="#ffffff">..please, Mum...</font>

29:15.520 --> 29:19.600
<font color="#ffffff">..give me a sign, just a small sign.</font>

29:22.320 --> 29:24.878
<font color="#ffffff">I don't want you</font>
<font color="#ffffff">to suffer like this.</font>

29:24.880 --> 29:26.560
<font color="#ffffff">I don't know what to do.</font>

29:35.000 --> 29:37.158
<font color="#00ffff">Who will look after...</font>

29:37.160 --> 29:39.320
<font color="#00ffff">..my Clarissa?</font>

29:52.400 --> 29:55.280
<font color="#ffff00">You won't be much use to her</font>
<font color="#ffff00">if you don't eat.</font>

29:58.680 --> 30:00.560
<font color="#ffffff">Not much use to her anyway.</font>

30:07.920 --> 30:09.840
<font color="#ffff00">Remember when I asked her?</font>

30:12.720 --> 30:14.160
<font color="#ffff00">If I could marry you?</font>

30:15.680 --> 30:17.440
<font color="#ffffff">She gave you such a grilling.</font>

30:18.840 --> 30:22.680
<font color="#ffffff">I thought you were going to give up</font>
<font color="#ffffff">on the whole thing. </font><font color="#ffff00">Nearly did.</font>

30:26.680 --> 30:28.920
<font color="#ffff00">I remember exactly what she said.</font>

30:30.600 --> 30:31.960
<font color="#ffff00">She said...</font>

30:37.240 --> 30:40.038
<font color="#ffff00">.."I'd say to take care of Clarissa.</font>

30:40.040 --> 30:42.998
<font color="#ffff00">"But she won't let you do that.</font>

30:43.000 --> 30:46.000
<font color="#ffff00">"And I'd say to always</font>
<font color="#ffff00">put her first.</font>

30:47.200 --> 30:49.920
<font color="#ffff00">"But she won't have any of that,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">either.</font>

30:51.880 --> 30:54.758
<font color="#ffff00">"Don't ever tell her want to do,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Max.</font>

30:54.760 --> 30:57.080
<font color="#ffff00">"She'll do the exact opposite."</font>

30:59.000 --> 31:00.680
<font color="#ffffff">Doesn't sound like me at all.</font>

31:04.240 --> 31:08.360
<font color="#ffff00">Her only advice was that we should</font>
<font color="#ffff00">stick together. And...</font>

31:09.920 --> 31:15.598
<font color="#ffff00">..she also told me that it was now</font>
<font color="#ffff00">my job to tell you</font>

31:15.600 --> 31:17.480
<font color="#ffff00">when you're being pig-headed.</font>

31:20.600 --> 31:22.640
<font color="#ffff00">You being pig-headed.</font>

31:25.440 --> 31:27.118
<font color="#ffff00">And, whatever you do,</font>

31:27.120 --> 31:28.480
<font color="#ffff00">don't eat this.</font>

31:36.440 --> 31:39.278
<font color="#00ffff">Grace was telling the truth</font>
<font color="#00ffff">about the note,</font>

31:39.280 --> 31:42.238
<font color="#00ffff">and there's no forensic evidence</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to place her</font>

31:42.240 --> 31:45.720
<font color="#00ffff">at the scene of Sue's death -</font>
<font color="#00ffff">wasn't her fingerprint.</font>

31:47.040 --> 31:51.720
<font color="#ffff00">Derek's death, Hope's abduction,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Sue's murder. They're all connected.</font>

31:53.080 --> 31:56.318
<font color="#ffff00">Does make me wonder if someone</font>
<font color="#ffff00">killed Sue to stop her revealing</font>

31:56.320 --> 31:59.078
<font color="#ffff00">the truth about the baby though.</font>

31:59.080 --> 32:01.398
<font color="#ffff00">I've been looking at the evidence</font>
<font color="#ffff00">again and I'm wondering</font>

32:01.400 --> 32:04.878
<font color="#ffff00">if the person we're looking for has</font>
<font color="#ffff00">some kind of medical background.</font>

32:04.880 --> 32:06.518
<font color="#00ff00">Medical? Why?</font>

32:06.520 --> 32:08.478
<font color="#ffff00">We found meds in Hope's system.</font>

32:08.480 --> 32:11.318
<font color="#ffff00">So, someone sourced and administered</font>
<font color="#ffff00">those drugs.</font>

32:11.320 --> 32:14.358
<font color="#ffff00">And we know from the bruising</font>
<font color="#ffff00">around the injection site</font>

32:14.360 --> 32:16.238
<font color="#ffff00">that Sue was sedated via syringe.</font>

32:16.240 --> 32:20.838
<font color="#00ffff">I identified the substance Clarissa</font>
<font color="#00ffff">lifted from Sue's clothes.</font>

32:20.840 --> 32:24.318
<font color="#00ffff">It's a glycerol-based compound.</font>

32:24.320 --> 32:27.358
<font color="#ffffff">Like the one Adam Brookham uses</font>
<font color="#ffffff">in his cryogenics process?</font>

32:27.360 --> 32:29.358
<font color="#00ffff">Identical, in fact.</font>

32:29.360 --> 32:34.800
<font color="#00ffff">Trace amounts likely transferred</font>
<font color="#00ffff">accidentally through contact.</font>

32:36.200 --> 32:39.038
<font color="#ffff00">The medical link could point to</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Adam too.</font>

32:39.040 --> 32:43.438
<font color="#ffff00">After all, he knows about anatomy,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">came from a medical background,</font>

32:43.440 --> 32:46.758
<font color="#ffff00">and he has access to purchasing</font>
<font color="#ffff00">all sorts of chemicals and drugs.</font>

32:46.760 --> 32:48.478
<font color="#ffff00">Why not for fluorouracil?</font>

32:48.480 --> 32:50.478
<font color="#00ff00">Adam's known Sue</font>
<font color="#00ff00">for more than 20 years.</font>

32:50.480 --> 32:52.718
<font color="#00ff00">He certainly knew all about</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Hope's illness.</font>

32:52.720 --> 32:54.878
<font color="#00ff00">Could he have been there</font>
<font color="#00ff00">when Sue died?</font>

32:54.880 --> 32:56.998
<font color="#ffffff">Sue's phone records have been</font>
<font color="#ffffff">released.</font>

32:57.000 --> 33:01.680
<font color="#ffffff">Her last contact was a text message</font>
<font color="#ffffff">she sent. Guess who it was to.</font>

33:06.600 --> 33:09.520
<font color="#ffff00">Well, let's bring him in.</font>

33:11.240 --> 33:13.958
<font color="#00ffff">It's a message from Sue,</font>

33:13.960 --> 33:17.678
<font color="#00ffff">but I didn't see it</font>
<font color="#00ffff">for at least an hour or so.</font>

33:17.680 --> 33:22.840
<font color="#00ff00">This is a partial fingerprint we</font>
<font color="#00ff00">found outside Sue Marshall's flat.</font>

33:24.200 --> 33:27.600
<font color="#ffff00">It is yours, so we can put</font>
<font color="#ffff00">you at the scene.</font>

33:28.720 --> 33:30.320
<font color="#00ffff">I was there. I won't deny it.</font>

33:31.760 --> 33:35.438
<font color="#00ffff">I thought the message was odd,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">so I went to check on her.</font>

33:35.440 --> 33:38.198
<font color="#ffff00">"Come quickly.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I want to be with Hope."</font>

33:38.200 --> 33:39.838
<font color="#00ffff">I looked through the window.</font>

33:39.840 --> 33:41.918
<font color="#00ffff">I saw that she was dead and...</font>

33:41.920 --> 33:44.718
<font color="#00ffff">..there was nothing</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I could do for her.</font>

33:44.720 --> 33:45.998
<font color="#ffff00">Call an ambulance?</font>

33:46.000 --> 33:47.598
<font color="#ffff00">Call the police?</font>

33:47.600 --> 33:51.278
<font color="#00ffff">Some people will stop at nothing</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to try and discredit my work.</font>

33:51.280 --> 33:54.158
<font color="#00ffff">I didn't want to give them</font>
<font color="#00ffff">any more ammunition.</font>

33:54.160 --> 33:56.880
<font color="#ffff00">Why did she contact you?</font>

33:58.120 --> 33:59.560
<font color="#00ffff">To begin the process.</font>

34:00.920 --> 34:02.558
<font color="#00ffff">But it was too late.</font>

34:02.560 --> 34:05.078
<font color="#00ffff">There was nothing I can do</font>
<font color="#00ffff">for somebody that far gone.</font>

34:05.080 --> 34:09.118
<font color="#00ffff">So, I left her there. I thought it</font>
<font color="#00ffff">best not to get involved.</font>

34:09.120 --> 34:11.918
<font color="#ffff00">You've got quite a history</font>
<font color="#ffff00">of that, haven't you?</font>

34:11.920 --> 34:13.520
<font color="#ffff00">Looking the other way.</font>

34:16.480 --> 34:20.038
<font color="#00ffff">If you're talking about a poor woman</font>
<font color="#00ffff">driven to take her own life, I think</font>

34:20.040 --> 34:23.239
<font color="#00ffff">I would look a little closer</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to home. </font><font color="#ffff00">Oh, yeah?</font>

34:25.440 --> 34:27.598
<font color="#00ffff">Sue Marshall was pretty upset when</font>
<font color="#00ffff">she thought</font>

34:27.600 --> 34:29.118
<font color="#00ffff">you wanted to hurt her daughter.</font>

34:29.120 --> 34:30.998
<font color="#ffff00">Only Hope wasn't her daughter.</font>

34:31.000 --> 34:32.277
<font color="#00ffff">What?</font>

34:32.280 --> 34:36.958
<font color="#ffff00">She was snatched from her real</font>
<font color="#ffff00">family when she was a baby.</font>

34:36.960 --> 34:38.197
<font color="#00ffff">I don't know about that.</font>

34:38.199 --> 34:40.080
<font color="#ffff00">And Sue didn't take her own life.</font>

34:41.520 --> 34:42.800
<font color="#ffff00">She was murdered.</font>

34:46.040 --> 34:49.158
<font color="#00ffff">Look, I didn't go inside the house.</font>

34:49.159 --> 34:51.719
<font color="#00ffff">I looked through the window</font>
<font color="#00ffff">and then I left.</font>

34:53.199 --> 34:54.918
<font color="#00ffff">If I thought she had been murdered,</font>

34:54.920 --> 34:56.998
<font color="#00ffff">of course I would've called</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the police.</font>

34:57.000 --> 34:59.918
<font color="#ffff00">Oh, that's very decent of you.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">The fact is you knew</font>

34:59.920 --> 35:02.998
<font color="#ffff00">a young girl had died</font>
<font color="#ffff00">in suspicious circumstances,</font>

35:03.000 --> 35:06.398
<font color="#ffff00">but you took the body. That's</font>
<font color="#ffff00">perverting the course of justice.</font>

35:06.400 --> 35:08.118
<font color="#00ffff">No, hang on a second.</font>

35:08.120 --> 35:09.920
<font color="#00ffff">I have not committed a crime!</font>

35:11.880 --> 35:13.838
<font color="#00ff00">I've been looking</font>
<font color="#00ff00">through your records.</font>

35:13.840 --> 35:16.358
<font color="#00ff00">You order cancer drugs on</font>
<font color="#00ff00">a regular basis, don't you?</font>

35:16.360 --> 35:19.678
<font color="#00ff00">Including fluorouracil.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">We're a research company.</font>

35:19.680 --> 35:22.398
<font color="#00ffff">We have vast amounts of cancerous</font>
<font color="#00ffff">tissue to do research on.</font>

35:22.400 --> 35:25.998
<font color="#ffff00">Did you supply the Marshalls</font>
<font color="#ffff00">with fluorouracil for Hope? </font><font color="#00ffff">What?</font>

35:26.000 --> 35:27.398
<font color="#00ffff">No!</font>

35:27.400 --> 35:28.878
<font color="#ffff00">I think you did.</font>

35:28.880 --> 35:32.758
<font color="#ffff00">Was Sue Marshall about to confess</font>
<font color="#ffff00">everything you'd done together?</font>

35:32.760 --> 35:35.318
<font color="#ffff00">She just made contact</font>
<font color="#ffff00">with Hope's birth mother.</font>

35:35.320 --> 35:37.758
<font color="#ffff00">Was she about to tell everyone</font>
<font color="#ffff00">that you froze Hope</font>

35:37.760 --> 35:40.238
<font color="#ffff00">before she was dead?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">That would be murder!</font>

35:40.240 --> 35:41.358
<font color="#ffff00">Did you? </font><font color="#00ffff">No!</font>

35:41.360 --> 35:43.718
<font color="#ffff00">But it is your ultimate</font>
<font color="#ffff00">ambition, isn't it?</font>

35:43.720 --> 35:46.798
<font color="#ffff00">You were working with a child</font>
<font color="#ffff00">nobody knew existed.</font>

35:46.800 --> 35:50.158
<font color="#ffff00">You could pretty much do what you</font>
<font color="#ffff00">wanted. Was she your lab rat?</font>

35:50.160 --> 35:51.920
<font color="#ffffff">HE BANGS HAND ON TABLE</font>

35:53.080 --> 35:54.678
<font color="#ffff00">Adam Brookham, I'm arresting you</font>

35:54.680 --> 35:56.998
<font color="#ffff00">for conspiracy to pervert</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the course of justice</font>

35:57.000 --> 35:59.600
<font color="#ffff00">and the suspected murder</font>
<font color="#ffff00">of Sue Marshall.</font>

36:03.600 --> 36:05.120
<font color="#ffffff">BUZZER</font>

36:22.080 --> 36:23.918
<font color="#ffffff">Hi, can I help me?</font>

36:23.920 --> 36:26.718
<font color="#ffff00">I'm Ann Carson. Erm...</font>

36:26.720 --> 36:30.118
<font color="#ffff00">Thomas Chamberlain asked me</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to come and sign some papers</font>

36:30.120 --> 36:32.238
<font color="#ffff00">to release my brother's body. </font><font color="#ffffff">Right.</font>

36:32.240 --> 36:34.358
<font color="#ffffff">Thomas isn't here right now.</font>

36:34.360 --> 36:35.800
<font color="#ffffff">SHE SIGHS</font>

36:37.320 --> 36:39.798
<font color="#ffff00">Should I come back?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">That might be best, if that's OK.</font>

36:39.800 --> 36:40.918
<font color="#ffffff">I'll get him to call.</font>

36:40.920 --> 36:44.598
<font color="#ffff00">I'm just quite keen to lay my</font>
<font color="#ffff00">brother's body to rest.</font>

36:44.600 --> 36:48.278
<font color="#ffff00">I don't like the idea of</font>
<font color="#ffff00">him being in here.</font>

36:48.280 --> 36:50.880
<font color="#ffff00">Maybe then we can all move on.</font>

36:52.600 --> 36:55.718
<font color="#ffffff">You've had a lot of shock recently,</font>

36:55.720 --> 36:58.758
<font color="#ffffff">especially finding out that Hope</font>
<font color="#ffffff">was...</font>

36:58.760 --> 37:01.798
<font color="#ffffff">It's a...it's an awful time</font>
<font color="#ffffff">for everyone involved.</font>

37:01.800 --> 37:05.238
<font color="#ffff00">Yeah. Especially for that poor mum.</font>

37:05.240 --> 37:09.198
<font color="#ffff00">Losing a baby like that, she was</font>
<font color="#ffff00">just a schoolgirl herself.</font>

37:09.200 --> 37:10.400
<font color="#ffff00">It's terrible.</font>

37:13.240 --> 37:18.438
<font color="#ffff00">Maybe they...maybe they were</font>
<font color="#ffff00">trying to help her in some way.</font>

37:18.440 --> 37:20.398
<font color="#ffff00">Sorry, are you OK?</font>

37:20.400 --> 37:22.480
<font color="#ffffff">SHE BREATHES HEAVILY</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Ch..chest</font>

37:23.800 --> 37:25.798
<font color="#ffff00">Here. </font><font color="#ffffff">Sorry, on my chest.</font>

37:25.800 --> 37:27.198
<font color="#ffff00">Let me help.</font>

37:27.200 --> 37:29.760
<font color="#ffffff">Does it feel like</font>
<font color="#ffffff">you're having a panic attack?</font>

37:31.720 --> 37:34.958
<font color="#ffff00">OK. Just it's going to pass.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">All right?</font>

37:34.960 --> 37:38.118
<font color="#ffff00">Nothing's going to happen. I'm going</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to stay with you. OK?</font>

37:38.120 --> 37:39.998
<font color="#ffff00">Just try and breathe with me.</font>

37:40.000 --> 37:41.438
<font color="#ffff00">OK?</font>

37:41.440 --> 37:43.518
<font color="#ffff00">Slowly. In, out.</font>

37:43.520 --> 37:45.038
<font color="#ffffff">SHE BREATHES OUT</font>

37:45.040 --> 37:46.398
<font color="#ffff00">That's it.</font>

37:46.400 --> 37:49.240
<font color="#ffff00">In...out.</font>

37:50.320 --> 37:51.360
<font color="#ffff00">OK?</font>

37:52.720 --> 37:54.198
<font color="#ffff00">Just feeling better?</font>

37:54.200 --> 37:55.760
<font color="#ffffff">I'm so sorry.</font>

37:57.120 --> 38:00.998
<font color="#ffff00">Don't be silly. You're having a</font>
<font color="#ffff00">stressful time at work.</font>

38:01.000 --> 38:04.238
<font color="#ffffff">Well, in truth, it's my mum.</font>

38:04.240 --> 38:05.400
<font color="#ffffff">She's...</font>

38:06.440 --> 38:07.480
<font color="#ffffff">She's dying.</font>

38:08.960 --> 38:10.000
<font color="#ffff00">I'm so sorry.</font>

38:11.120 --> 38:15.720
<font color="#ffffff">End-stage cancer.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">That is so stressful.</font>

38:18.320 --> 38:21.558
<font color="#ffffff">You're a good person to have around</font>
<font color="#ffffff">in a crisis.</font>

38:21.560 --> 38:22.920
<font color="#ffffff">I'll remember that.</font>

38:24.360 --> 38:26.240
<font color="#ffffff">You must be medically trained.</font>

38:27.680 --> 38:29.120
<font color="#ffff00">Erm...</font>

38:31.240 --> 38:32.920
<font color="#ffff00">I'm a...</font>

38:34.200 --> 38:35.920
<font color="#ffff00">..an accountant.</font>

38:37.280 --> 38:41.400
<font color="#ffff00">The only thing I can resuscitate</font>
<font color="#ffff00">are your books!</font>

38:42.760 --> 38:45.800
<font color="#ffffff">You, er, seemed</font>
<font color="#ffffff">so confident though.</font>

38:47.200 --> 38:52.158
<font color="#ffff00">Erm, well, I did dip</font>
<font color="#ffff00">my toe into nursing.</font>

38:52.160 --> 38:54.600
<font color="#ffff00">You know, many moons ago. Erm...</font>

38:56.320 --> 38:59.158
<font color="#ffff00">..I did a little training,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">but it wasn't for me.</font>

38:59.160 --> 39:04.760
<font color="#ffffff">I suppose that sort of training</font>
<font color="#ffffff">stays with you. </font><font color="#ffff00">Yeah. Suppose so.</font>

39:10.600 --> 39:12.160
<font color="#ffffff">You've hurt your hand.</font>

39:13.360 --> 39:16.038
<font color="#ffff00">I burned myself. </font><font color="#ffffff">How did you do it?</font>

39:16.040 --> 39:17.998
<font color="#ffff00">Boiling water.</font>

39:18.000 --> 39:20.278
<font color="#ffff00">I wasn't paying attention.</font>

39:20.280 --> 39:22.158
<font color="#ffff00">It's this business with my brother.</font>

39:22.160 --> 39:24.158
<font color="#ffff00">Finding out that he...</font>

39:24.160 --> 39:26.360
<font color="#ffff00">..he took his own life.</font>

39:27.800 --> 39:29.478
<font color="#ffff00">It's changed everything.</font>

39:29.480 --> 39:31.800
<font color="#ffffff">I'm sure it has.</font>

39:46.240 --> 39:47.800
<font color="#ffff00">Erm...</font>

39:49.400 --> 39:51.640
<font color="#ffff00">..it's just a thought,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">about your poor mum.</font>

39:53.520 --> 39:58.438
<font color="#ffff00">I've got a friend who has links to</font>
<font color="#ffff00">a pharmaceutical company.</font>

39:58.440 --> 40:01.198
<font color="#ffff00">I mean, maybe my friend</font>
<font color="#ffff00">could get her onto</font>

40:01.200 --> 40:04.438
<font color="#ffff00">one of these new drugs trials,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">you know,</font>

40:04.440 --> 40:06.998
<font color="#ffff00">they're extremely difficult</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to get onto.</font>

40:07.000 --> 40:08.638
<font color="#ffff00">Maybe...</font>

40:08.640 --> 40:10.480
<font color="#ffff00">..I could pull a few strings?</font>

40:13.080 --> 40:16.240
<font color="#ffffff">Did your friend get cancer</font>
<font color="#ffffff">drugs for Hope too?</font>

40:18.120 --> 40:19.758
<font color="#ffff00">Sorry, I don't understand.</font>

40:19.760 --> 40:22.878
<font color="#ffffff">You know, someone gave Hope</font>
<font color="#ffffff">the wrong cancer treatment.</font>

40:22.880 --> 40:25.918
<font color="#ffffff">If they'd given her</font>
<font color="#ffffff">the right medication,</font>

40:25.920 --> 40:27.840
<font color="#ffffff">she could have been saved.</font>

40:32.640 --> 40:36.118
<font color="#ffff00">Listen, your mum is really sick,</font>

40:36.120 --> 40:38.160
<font color="#ffff00">by the sound of things.</font>

40:39.960 --> 40:42.160
<font color="#ffff00">I wouldn't leave it too long.</font>

40:57.240 --> 40:59.360
<font color="#ffffff">GENTLE SNORING</font>

41:37.800 --> 41:40.440
<font color="#ffffff">I don't believe it.</font>

41:49.160 --> 41:50.360
<font color="#ffffff">We need to talk.</font>

41:51.640 --> 41:54.798
<font color="#ffffff">There was no way Ann could have</font>
<font color="#ffffff">known Grace was a schoolgirl</font>

41:54.800 --> 41:57.518
<font color="#ffffff">when she gave birth.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">It wasn't in any of the papers.</font>

41:57.520 --> 42:00.158
<font color="#ffffff">The only way she could have known</font>
<font color="#ffffff">is by being there.</font>

42:00.160 --> 42:05.078
<font color="#ffffff">And look. Look at the health</font>
<font color="#ffffff">visitor's comments.</font>

42:05.080 --> 42:08.998
<font color="#ffffff">"Newly widowed. I'm concerned about</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Ann's capability</font>

42:09.000 --> 42:12.838
<font color="#ffffff">"to look after this newborn son</font>
<font color="#ffffff">and seven-month-old little girl</font>

42:12.840 --> 42:15.078
<font color="#ffffff">"she's already taking care of."</font>

42:15.080 --> 42:17.758
<font color="#ffffff">Ann is the link to Adam Brookham.</font>

42:17.760 --> 42:19.478
<font color="#ffffff">She had fertility treatment there.</font>

42:19.480 --> 42:22.120
<font color="#ffffff">That's how she gave birth</font>
<font color="#ffffff">to her only son, Mark.</font>

42:24.000 --> 42:25.918
<font color="#ffff00">Clarissa, what are you doing?</font>

42:25.920 --> 42:29.518
<font color="#ffffff">I did some digging around last</font>
<font color="#ffffff">night. Ann was an agency nurse</font>

42:29.520 --> 42:32.358
<font color="#ffffff">back in the day and did, in</font>
<font color="#ffffff">fact, take some shifts</font>

42:32.360 --> 42:34.358
<font color="#ffffff">at the Travis Maternity Hospital</font>

42:34.360 --> 42:37.078
<font color="#ffffff">while she was training.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Ann knew the hospital.</font>

42:37.080 --> 42:38.278
<font color="#ffffff">She had the uniform.</font>

42:38.280 --> 42:40.158
<font color="#ffffff">She could have blended in.</font>

42:40.160 --> 42:43.478
<font color="#ffffff">What if she snatched Hope</font>
<font color="#ffffff">with Derek?</font>

42:43.480 --> 42:46.358
<font color="#ffff00">That's quite a leap. </font><font color="#ffffff">Is it?</font>

42:46.360 --> 42:50.518
<font color="#ffffff">We know Ann wanted children and must</font>
<font color="#ffffff">have had problems conceiving.</font>

42:50.520 --> 42:55.358
<font color="#ffffff">Her husband died, along with</font>
<font color="#ffffff">her chances of conceiving naturally.</font>

42:55.360 --> 42:59.358
<font color="#ffffff">Maybe she killed Sue to stop</font>
<font color="#ffffff">her revealing the truth.</font>

42:59.360 --> 43:02.478
<font color="#ffffff">Ann always thought</font>
<font color="#ffffff">she was a loose cannon.</font>

43:02.480 --> 43:06.518
<font color="#ffffff">She was incensed by the way</font>
<font color="#ffffff">that Derek's body had been treated.</font>

43:06.520 --> 43:10.638
<font color="#ffffff">If she knew that was Sue... </font><font color="#ffff00">Ann has</font>
<font color="#ffff00">an alibi for the time of the murder.</font>

43:10.640 --> 43:12.838
<font color="#ffff00">I had it checked out.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Check it again.</font>

43:12.840 --> 43:15.198
<font color="#ffffff">She's had medical training.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">She had access to drugs.</font>

43:15.200 --> 43:18.998
<font color="#ffffff">It all fits. </font><font color="#ffff00">We have Adam Brookham</font>
<font color="#ffff00">in custody for Sue's murder.</font>

43:19.000 --> 43:20.998
<font color="#ffff00">We have his fingerprint</font>
<font color="#ffff00">at the scene.</font>

43:21.000 --> 43:24.560
<font color="#ffffff">Maybe he didn't go inside</font>
<font color="#ffffff">the flat, just as he claimed.</font>

43:26.480 --> 43:28.198
<font color="#ffff00">What are you asking?</font>

43:28.200 --> 43:30.398
<font color="#ffffff">Ann has a bandage on her right hand.</font>

43:30.400 --> 43:34.438
<font color="#ffffff">She says it's a burn. What if she</font>
<font color="#ffffff">cut herself when she murdered Sue?</font>

43:34.440 --> 43:35.918
<font color="#ffff00">OK, stop.</font>

43:35.920 --> 43:38.158
<font color="#ffff00">I interviewed her the day</font>
<font color="#ffff00">after the murder.</font>

43:38.160 --> 43:39.798
<font color="#ffff00">There was no bandage on her hand.</font>

43:39.800 --> 43:43.158
<font color="#ffffff">Well, it could have been a small cut</font>
<font color="#ffffff">that became infected later on.</font>

43:43.160 --> 43:47.198
<font color="#ffff00">Clarissa! </font><font color="#ffffff">You are duty-bound</font>
<font color="#ffffff">to investigate this case to the best</font>

43:47.200 --> 43:50.640
<font color="#ffffff">of your ability, and that includes</font>
<font color="#ffffff">following up on my leads!</font>

43:52.680 --> 43:55.198
<font color="#ffff00">You had fertility treatment</font>
<font color="#ffff00">with Dr Adam Brookham.</font>

43:55.200 --> 43:56.520
<font color="#ffff00">Is that correct?</font>

43:58.960 --> 44:01.838
<font color="#00ffff">I miscarried three babies.</font>

44:01.840 --> 44:03.120
<font color="#00ffff">Three.</font>

44:05.320 --> 44:07.438
<font color="#00ffff">It's not a crime, is it?</font>

44:07.440 --> 44:10.998
<font color="#00ffff">I want to have a family.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">And Adam Brookham helped you.</font>

44:11.000 --> 44:12.878
<font color="#00ffff">Yes.</font>

44:12.880 --> 44:15.680
<font color="#00ffff">He's a brilliant man.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">He's brilliant.</font>

44:17.200 --> 44:19.358
<font color="#00ffff">I wouldn't have my son</font>
<font color="#00ffff">if it wasn't for him.</font>

44:19.360 --> 44:21.278
<font color="#00ffff">I owe him everything.</font>

44:21.280 --> 44:23.720
<font color="#ffff00">Did you introduce</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Sue and Derek to Adam?</font>

44:26.400 --> 44:28.118
<font color="#00ffff">Yeah. Erm...</font>

44:28.120 --> 44:31.678
<font color="#00ffff">..Adam came to my son's first</font>
<font color="#00ffff">birthday party.</font>

44:31.680 --> 44:34.640
<font color="#ffff00">You trained as a nurse,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I understand.</font>

44:35.800 --> 44:39.398
<font color="#00ffff">Yes, for a couple of years.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Erm, it wasn't for me.</font>

44:39.400 --> 44:42.758
<font color="#00ffff">I didn't even fully qualify.</font>

44:42.760 --> 44:45.920
<font color="#ffff00">Did you work at</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the Travis Maternity Hospital?</font>

44:47.360 --> 44:52.718
<font color="#00ffff">Yes. When you, when you're a</font>
<font color="#00ffff">trainee, you have to move around and</font>
<font color="#00ffff">we all</font>

44:52.720 --> 44:55.038
<font color="#00ffff">had to do shifts on maternity.</font>

44:55.040 --> 44:59.918
<font color="#ffffff">The health visitor's report from</font>
<font color="#ffffff">after your son was born states</font>

44:59.920 --> 45:02.800
<font color="#ffffff">there was a seven-month-old</font>
<font color="#ffffff">little girl living with you.</font>

45:04.920 --> 45:08.080
<font color="#00ffff">Oh, yes. Yes. Hope.</font>

45:09.400 --> 45:12.480
<font color="#ffff00">So, why was Hope living with you?</font>

45:14.200 --> 45:17.878
<font color="#00ffff">Well, I told you, Sue was a mess.</font>

45:17.880 --> 45:19.958
<font color="#00ffff">I was just being kind.</font>

45:19.960 --> 45:22.318
<font color="#00ffff">I wanted to take the pressure</font>
<font color="#00ffff">off my brother.</font>

45:22.320 --> 45:25.638
<font color="#00ffff">And then, when Mark came along,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I couldn't cope with both.</font>

45:25.640 --> 45:28.880
<font color="#00ffff">So, Derek took Hope back home.</font>

45:33.680 --> 45:35.158
<font color="#00ffff">Sorry, what...</font>

45:35.160 --> 45:36.798
<font color="#00ffff">..what is all this about?</font>

45:36.800 --> 45:39.838
<font color="#ffff00">Would you mind removing the bandage</font>
<font color="#ffff00">from your hand, please?</font>

45:39.840 --> 45:41.438
<font color="#00ffff">Why?</font>

45:41.440 --> 45:43.840
<font color="#ffff00">Well, I'm interested to see</font>
<font color="#ffff00">how you hurt it.</font>

45:46.240 --> 45:48.238
<font color="#00ffff">It's...it's a burn.</font>

45:48.240 --> 45:50.518
<font color="#ffff00">Well, then our police surgeon</font>
<font color="#ffff00">can remove it for you</font>

45:50.520 --> 45:52.760
<font color="#ffff00">and we'll get all this</font>
<font color="#ffff00">cleared up straight away.</font>

45:56.800 --> 45:58.078
<font color="#00ffff">All right.</font>

45:58.080 --> 46:00.280
<font color="#ffff00">She'll even put on a fresh one</font>
<font color="#ffff00">for you.</font>

46:20.680 --> 46:22.120
<font color="#00ffff">Satisfied now?</font>

46:24.200 --> 46:26.600
<font color="#ffff00">I am so sorry to have troubled you.</font>

46:47.080 --> 46:49.798
<font color="#ffff00">Look, I'm not going to tell</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Thomas about this.</font>

46:49.800 --> 46:51.478
<font color="#ffffff">I haven't done anything wrong.</font>

46:51.480 --> 46:53.758
<font color="#ffff00">Then why did you come directly</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to me with your theory?</font>

46:53.760 --> 46:55.280
<font color="#ffff00">Why didn't you go through him?</font>

46:59.280 --> 47:00.600
<font color="#ffff00">Clarissa...</font>

47:01.800 --> 47:03.798
<font color="#ffff00">..I know you've got stuff going on,</font>

47:03.800 --> 47:06.240
<font color="#ffff00">but you need to sort yourself out.</font>

47:09.280 --> 47:10.640
<font color="#ffff00">Thanks.</font>

47:12.920 --> 47:14.120
<font color="#00ffff">Come on, then.</font>

47:28.400 --> 47:31.278
<font color="#00ffff">If it was Thomas she'd called and</font>
<font color="#00ffff">not me, you'd be getting</font>

47:31.280 --> 47:32.598
<font color="#00ffff">the third degree by now.</font>

47:32.600 --> 47:34.878
<font color="#ffffff">Why can't you all just let me</font>
<font color="#ffffff">get on with my work?</font>

47:34.880 --> 47:38.438
<font color="#00ffff">You should be spending all your time</font>
<font color="#00ffff">with your mum while you still can.</font>

47:38.440 --> 47:41.118
<font color="#ffffff">She doesn't even know</font>
<font color="#ffffff">who I am, Jack.</font>

47:41.120 --> 47:43.918
<font color="#ffffff">She barely knows who she is.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">What are we meant to do?</font>

47:43.920 --> 47:46.678
<font color="#ffffff">Just stare each other in silence</font>
<font color="#ffffff">day after day?</font>

47:46.680 --> 47:51.038
<font color="#ffffff">I don't even get to say goodbye</font>
<font color="#ffffff">to her, because she's already gone.</font>

47:51.040 --> 47:54.798
<font color="#ffffff">It makes no difference</font>
<font color="#ffffff">to her if I'm there or not.</font>

47:54.800 --> 47:57.118
<font color="#00ffff">But it makes a difference to you.</font>

47:57.120 --> 48:00.118
<font color="#00ffff">You won't get this time again.</font>

48:00.120 --> 48:02.118
<font color="#00ffff">Don't live with regret.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">She's your mum.</font>

48:02.120 --> 48:04.760
<font color="#ffffff">I thought you, of all people,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">had my back.</font>

48:17.760 --> 48:19.880
<font color="#ffffff">I'm sorry.</font>

48:36.680 --> 48:38.600
<font color="#ffff00">Clarissa, what can I do for you?</font>

48:42.120 --> 48:44.320
<font color="#ffffff">I think I should take some time off.</font>

48:46.840 --> 48:50.600
<font color="#ffff00">OK. OK, I'll arrange</font>
<font color="#ffff00">cover from...from tomorrow.</font>

48:52.320 --> 48:56.040
<font color="#ffff00">Take as long as you need, yeah?</font>
<font color="#ffff00">We're here whenever you need us.</font>

49:02.160 --> 49:03.600
<font color="#00ffff">Need a hand?</font>

49:11.000 --> 49:12.960
<font color="#ffffff">Ever since I was little...</font>

49:13.960 --> 49:16.438
<font color="#ffffff">..it's always just been me and Mum.</font>

49:16.440 --> 49:18.200
<font color="#ffffff">She's the one constant I've had.</font>

49:19.640 --> 49:21.880
<font color="#ffffff">Soon, she won't be here any more.</font>

49:24.000 --> 49:26.360
<font color="#ffffff">And it's sort of terrifying.</font>

49:27.920 --> 49:29.200
<font color="#00ffff">Yeah.</font>

49:31.280 --> 49:32.880
<font color="#00ffff">I got your back.</font>

50:17.560 --> 50:20.118
<font color="#ffffff">It's a match, wild parsnip sap.</font>

50:20.120 --> 50:21.958
<font color="#ffffff">I've called DI Raymond.</font>

50:21.960 --> 50:27.118
<font color="#ffff00">I don't...I don't understand.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Well, you can clearly see</font>

50:27.120 --> 50:30.038
<font color="#ffffff">wild parsnips stems broken</font>
<font color="#ffffff">beneath Sue's window.</font>

50:30.040 --> 50:31.998
<font color="#ffffff">The sap is highly toxic.</font>

50:32.000 --> 50:35.078
<font color="#ffffff">If it comes into contact</font>
<font color="#ffffff">with the skin when exposed to bright</font>

50:35.080 --> 50:38.718
<font color="#ffffff">sunlight, skin will burn</font>
<font color="#ffffff">horribly and blister.</font>

50:38.720 --> 50:42.038
<font color="#ffffff">That's why Ann's burn</font>
<font color="#ffffff">didn't show up immediately.</font>

50:42.040 --> 50:45.398
<font color="#ffffff">And why her hand wasn't bandaged</font>
<font color="#ffffff">when DI Raymond</font>

50:45.400 --> 50:47.038
<font color="#ffffff">interviewed her the next day.</font>

50:47.040 --> 50:49.518
<font color="#ffffff">Ann must have left via the window,</font>

50:49.520 --> 50:54.038
<font color="#ffffff">broken the stems and the sap</font>
<font color="#ffffff">transferred to her hand.</font>

50:54.040 --> 50:56.758
<font color="#00ff00">Oh, this area. </font><font color="#00ffff">Brilliant,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">thank you so much.</font>

50:56.760 --> 50:59.480
<font color="#ffffff">POLICE SIRENS BLARE</font>

51:02.280 --> 51:04.920
<font color="#ffff00">Right, Scott, around the back.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Paul, with me.</font>

51:07.760 --> 51:09.760
<font color="#00ffff">Mrs Carson! It's the police!</font>

51:11.040 --> 51:12.240
<font color="#ffff00">OK. Paul.</font>

51:14.000 --> 51:16.520
<font color="#ffff00">Right. Quinn, upstairs. </font><font color="#00ff00">Gov.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Check in there.</font>

51:29.120 --> 51:30.598
<font color="#00ff00">Clear, Gov!</font>

51:30.600 --> 51:32.000
<font color="#00ffff">Clear, Gov!</font>

51:37.920 --> 51:39.718
<font color="#ffff00">Clarissa, yeah, I need your help.</font>

51:39.720 --> 51:41.038
<font color="#ffffff">OK, hold on.</font>

51:41.040 --> 51:44.118
<font color="#00ffff">I'll wager this will have traces of</font>
<font color="#00ffff">sedative and Sue's blood on it.</font>

51:44.120 --> 51:45.160
<font color="#ffff00">Good.</font>

51:46.120 --> 51:47.918
<font color="#00ff00">Put out a call to pick her up.</font>

51:47.920 --> 51:50.598
<font color="#00ff00">But she's disappeared, Gov.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">CLARISSA: I might have something.</font>

51:50.600 --> 51:52.758
<font color="#ffff00">Come on, Clarissa,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">what can you give me?</font>

51:52.760 --> 51:56.518
<font color="#ffffff">Ann doesn't know she needs to</font>
<font color="#ffffff">hide, so her mobile's on.</font>

51:56.520 --> 51:58.598
<font color="#ffffff">I'm tracking her GPS.</font>

51:58.600 --> 52:01.920
<font color="#ffffff">Honing in on the signal now.</font>

52:06.120 --> 52:09.040
<font color="#ffffff">She's at Heathrow Airport,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Terminal 5.</font>

52:15.080 --> 52:17.478
<font color="#ffffff">PILOT: </font><font color="#00ffff">Good afternoon,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">ladies and gentlemen,</font>

52:17.480 --> 52:19.280
<font color="#00ffff">and welcome aboard this flight...</font>

52:23.800 --> 52:26.438
<font color="#ffffff">PILOT: </font><font color="#00ffff">Flight time is an hour</font>
<font color="#00ffff">and 15 minutes.</font>

52:26.440 --> 52:28.438
<font color="#00ff00">Police! Coming through!</font>

52:28.440 --> 52:31.280
<font color="#ffff00">Excuse me! </font><font color="#00ff00">Get out of the way,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">please! Thank you.</font>

52:37.920 --> 52:40.278
<font color="#ffffff">PA: </font><font color="#ffff00">Thank you very</font>
<font color="#ffff00">much, ladies and gents.</font>

52:40.280 --> 52:41.958
<font color="#ffff00">Please can you make sure</font>
<font color="#ffff00">your seat belts</font>

52:41.960 --> 52:44.038
<font color="#ffff00">are securely fastened,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">tray tables stowed away,</font>

52:44.040 --> 52:46.438
<font color="#ffff00">and your seats are in the upright</font>
<font color="#ffff00">position for take-off?</font>

